{
  "stem": "523.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time-- it sounds funny now-- but if she gave me a little piece of bread, I remember she used to cook borscht all day long.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this-- borscht, a luxury-- a piece of bread with borscht-- this is-- this-- this was I working for.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I endangered my life many times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She used to give me home some food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I used to take to my brother into the factory to give him something to eat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my brother used to-- there was pieces of wood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He used to tie it down around my waist under my shawl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I had a shawl, I like a piece of rag to keep me warm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I used to go out from the gate.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Sometimes the-- what standing at the gate, he use-- he realized that I have some wood, something hidden.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He didn't pay any attention.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Some-- one of them [INAUDIBLE], and he opened that piece of rag, saw the pieces of wood tied to my naked body.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He used to tear it off together with my skin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was the life in Bershad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One incident, when the Russians started already to attack, come closer, until then we had the Romanian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the Capitain Generale used to hang Jewish people on the trees.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they were hanging for days, dangling there on the trees.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then when the Germans came already closer became life even more terrible, because the SS already.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I remember one night, I had to go to the washroom, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We didn't had any washroom, so we had to go out outside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this was in the night in the snow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was practically naked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The minute I went out, I saw the German patrol coming close.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was 11 years old by then.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
